title: The Data Protector (Chapter1-2) - Part1 of a 2-Chapter Series
description:
This is part1 of the entire 2-chapter chapter series

A young man named Brian McGraw fell madly in love with Rachael Maria and never wants to let her go but she didn't love him and in the end lost her out of betrayal and now he his spirit is so broken his health deteriorated until he meets his fate of becoming the old and legendary Data Protector, what lies ahead of him other then misery, and heartbreak. Grab a copy of this book/ebook to find out.

Also on scribd, mininova, and vertor.
